{
  "stem": "18778.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was still alive at that time, but she didn't feel up to it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The youngest was a 51-year-old very beautiful woman who was a baby on the arms of her parents on the ship.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somebody had brought photographs and we were looking at photographs from the ship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she said, oh, that's me and my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She saw herself on the arms of her parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had ended up in France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When the Germans invaded, her parents had given her to a farmer, had informed relatives here in this country that they have given the child to this farmer.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the parents perished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After the war, the uncle and aunt came to France and found her and took her back to the States and raised her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was one of the outstanding things of our visit to Miami.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the unpleasant things that happened was that this politician somehow had found what was supposed to be Adolf Hitler's yacht was a wreck.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they wanted to blow it up in front of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we really did not like this particular part of our visit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he also arranged for a private yacht to take us to the spot where the passed out to sea a little bit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was just as I remembered how close we were to the beach and to Collins Avenue and to the hotels.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, now there are many more than there were then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was such a friendly scene that we saw as we passed by and were followed by the military plane so many years ago.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had on board some of this politician's supporters as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But otherwise, just the survivors.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
